data.description: This is a great home located next to Desert Harbor Community and walking distance from the school.  Single level, 2 car garage, 4 bedrooms and a large family room as well as living room. Open kitchen features oak cabinets with 2 year old stainless appliances.  Primary bedroom has its own private bath with separate tub and shower as well as a walk-in closet. Other 3 bedrooms are located on the south wing of the house providing perfect privacy. Water heater less than 2 years old. Garage door opener less than a year old. Air conditioning unit installed 3 years ago has a 10 year service warranty. Backyard has covered patio and plenty of space for entertainment. This home is a MUST SEE
